*****************************************
Developers information - Sesmo-VLAB (SVL)
*****************************************

Variable and Classe names:
--------------------------
A) Variable name should began with upper case letter and be self-understandable. Each new word began with a uppercase letter. 
Exemples : int myInteger; vector<double> VectorOfPointer; etc.

B) Class attribute should be self-understandable. 
Exemples : int NumberOfLayers; Element ShellOf4Nodes; etc.

C) Class name should began with an uppercase Letter.
Exemples : class MyClass;

D) Element/Material/Section class file name has the following structure: Formulation-Dimension-Name-nNodes.hpp
Exemples : lin2DQuad4.hpp, fb3DCircular.hpp, Elastic3DLinear.hpp  

Standart Doxygen comments
-------------------------
To automatise code documentation, comments should be insert as follow in header files.

A) At the head of files
/// @author    authors names
/// @date      12 Novembre 2009
/// @version   1.0
/// @file      file name
/// @brief     brief description

B) Before class definition
/// @class     class name
/// @brief     brief descritption
/// @details    Detailed description
///                  continue description

C) Before function and method prototypes
/// brief description
/// @details    Detailed description
///                  continue description
/// @param      parameter name and description
/// @return     return description
/// @see        relation with other classes

D) Class member descrption
/// member description
type variable; 

Developer personnal comments - flags
-------------------------------------

Key word list :     
//DEV:    in developement
//TODO:   should be done in the future
//ERROR:  error : to correct ASAP
//VERIF:  to verify : is it needed ?
//TEST:   test : To delete ASAP

-----For each modification, a comment should be prepared to be included to the commit message for Git.
